Her mother was the famed bard [[Talanthe Truesilver]], composer of "[[The Ballad of the Dream Weaver]]".The Truesilver name suggests a connection to the [[Truesilver]] noble house of [[Cormyr]], but this may just be coincidental. She was a cousin of [[Lisyil Sweetwhisper]], the herald to High Lord [[Kalahar Twohands]] of Loudwater.{{Cite web/Legacy of the Green Regent/"Humility" Plot Recap}}
